- further optimize branch/label handling to use local position vars instead of
  a hash table/linked list entry search, when possible. See the first
  3 commits from the asml branch. but this is too complicated. a
  local var is enough to hold a label position, which can be patched
  in a branch insn withint the same block.
- add -O2 passes, like -finline and -funroll, but no need for SSA analysis (yet).
- for the CTFE check, set more pure attributes to known library function calls,
  which are pure in the given arguments. observe the purity of calls in CTFE
- optional QBE backend for -O2?
- SSA conversion for -O2?
- Missing C23 features (https://en.cppreference.com/c/compiler_support/23):
  _BitInt, decimal, interchange and extended float types, FENV_ACCESS.
  But for larger codegen changes extract them into extra files.
  vector support is already too much for codegen.c, and can be extracted into
  an extra c file.
